        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="chu">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/> <persName ref="names.xml#n017">савн</persName>
                    <lb n="2"/> <persName ref="names.xml#n018">нфонть</persName>
                    <lb n="3"/> <orig>іх</orig> <persName ref="names.xml#n019">калнкь</persName> <orig>п</orig> 
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <head xml:lang="bg">Букви в лигатура:</head> 
                    <head xml:lang="en">Letters in ligatures:</head>
                         <app loc="1"> <note>ав (савн)</note></app>
                         <app loc="2"> <note>н (нфонть)</note></app>
                         <app loc="3"> <note>нк (калнкь)</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <seg xml:lang="bg"> 
                            Савин
                            Нифонт
                    ...их Калиник пи...
                </seg>
                <seg xml:lang="en"> 
                            Savin
                            Nifont
                    ...их Kalinik пи...
                </seg>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>
                    <seg xml:lang="bg"><note>Според Н. Ангелов последният ред може да се възстанови по следния начин: "[азъ мн]х(ъ) калнкъ пса(хъ)"(Ангелов 1985:242).</note></seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en"><note>According to N. Angelov, the last line can be reconstructed as follows: "[азъ мн]х(ъ) калнкъ пса(хъ)" (Angelov 1985:242)</note></seg>
                </p> 
            </div>
